rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0001
rows.name: Everybody set?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0002
rows.name: Yes, sir! Ready to go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0003
rows.name: Someone's excited.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0004
rows.name: Just doin' my job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0005
rows.name:
Speaking of which, it's pretty amazing
you made White Whale crew, at your age...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0006
rows.name: You have family here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0007
rows.name: My Mom and Dad passed away. They didn't make it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0008
rows.name: Ah...that day? The attack on Earth?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0009
rows.name: No, sir. It was before that. An accident.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0010
rows.name: Ah. I'm sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0011
rows.name: It's okay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0012
rows.name:
My parents were both design engineers
who worked on the White Whale project.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0013
rows.name: But there was a mishap with the primary engine test...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0014
rows.name:
Still, it's thanks to them, and people like them,
that the rest of us are all still here, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0015
rows.name: They made the White Whale spaceworthy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0015_2
rows.name:
So they didn't die in vain.
At least, that's what I like to think.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0016
rows.name: I see...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0017
rows.name:
So they gave you a spot on the White Whale to say thanks—
thanks to your parents for all their hard work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0018
rows.name: It's a debt I try to repay every day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0019
rows.name: Helping out folks any way I can.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0020
rows.name: Don't misunderstand, Lao.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0021
rows.name:
Lin earned her spot on the crew like anyone else.
It was her talent and determination that made it happen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0022
rows.name:
Her parents' positions provided an environment
for her to learn in, but that's it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0023
rows.name: Lin got to where she is now entirely on her own.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0024
rows.name: It's okay, Elma...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0025
rows.name:
No, she's right. Sometimes I talk before thinking.
Sorry about that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0026
rows.name: Don't be silly—you don't need to apologize to me, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06060100_MSG0027
rows.name: Now, shall we get going?[ST:wait ]
